        About this item

        • Lions Mane Capsules for Brain & Immune Support: Made using hand-picked Lions Mane mushroom extract, our supplement provides impressive benefits to support cognitive function and overall well-being.
        • Organic Mushroom Extract: Our mushroom capsules are only made from 100% mushrooms (fruiting bodies), not mycelium grown on grain like most brands. It contains no grains, additives, or fillers.
        • Measured Beta-Glucans: Verified by 3rd-party labs, our organic mushroom supplement has >30% beta-glucans per capsule, helping to naturally support your immune system.
        • How to Take: Adults take 2 capsules daily. You can also break a few capsules open and add them to your meal or drink. Our mushroom beta glucan supplements are gluten-free, non-GMO, & vegan.
        • Mushrooms Made Real: At Real Mushrooms, we produce organic mushroom supplements that support overall health. Our products contain 100% organic mushrooms, carefully sourced and processed for potency & efficacy.

            Safety Information

            These statements have not been evaluated by the Food and Drug Administration. This product is not intended to diagnose, treat, cure, or prevent any disease. Keep out of reach of children. Consult a physician if you are pregnant or nursing; have or had a medical condition, or are taking prescription drugs. There's a very small percentage of people who may experience allergy type symptoms from consuming mushrooms. This could include upset stomach, skin irritation, and headaches. This may be product specific or dose dependent. It is advised to stop consuming the product if you do not feel well. If you wish to try the product again, start with a smaller dose.

            Indications

            For use as a dietary supplement.

            Ingredients

            Hot water extracted organic lions mane mushrooms

            Directions

            For use as a dietary supplement. Adults take 2 capsules per day.

            Legal Disclaimer

            These statements have not been evaluated by the Food and Drug Administration. This product is not intended to diagnose, treat, cure, or prevent any disease. Consult a physician if you are pregnant or nursing; have or had a medical condition, or are taking prescription drugs. If you encounter adverse effects, stop taking the product immediately.

            How customer reviews and ratings work

            Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

            To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

            Unlocking Mental Clarity: Lion's Mane & Super Cocoa
            Having explored the benefits of both Lions Mane and Super Cocoa, I must say that Super Cocoa emerges as the ultimate champion, delivering a unique blend of nootropic benefits, exceptional flavor, sustained energy, and a delightful coffee alternative. However, let's not undermine the value of Lions Mane, as it remains an excellent supplement in its own right.Let's start with Lions Mane. This remarkable supplement is derived from a medicinal mushroom and has gained popularity for its potential cognitive-enhancing properties. Lions Mane contains compounds that may support brain health, including hericenones and erinacines. It has been associated with improved focus, memory, and overall cognitive function. Taking Lions Mane as a supplement can be beneficial for those seeking a natural boost to their mental capabilities.On the other hand, Super Cocoa takes the concept of a coffee alternative to new heights by combining nootropic ingredients with a delicious taste. Super Cocoa offers a unique blend of l-theanine, rhodiola, l-tyrosine, and alpha GPC. L-theanine promotes relaxation and mental clarity, while rhodiola is known for its adaptogenic properties, helping the body better cope with stress. L-tyrosine supports dopamine production, which aids in focus and mood enhancement. Alpha GPC is a cholinergic compound that may enhance cognitive function and memory.What truly sets Super Cocoa apart is not only its nootropic ingredients but also its exceptional flavor and sustained energy without the crash. Super Cocoa provides an indulgent taste, reminiscent of a premium coffee blend, which makes it a delightful treat for the senses. The absence of artificial sweeteners or flavors ensures a more natural and authentic experience. Moreover, the combination of nootropic ingredients in Super Cocoa ensures sustained mental stamina, avoiding the crash that is commonly associated with traditional energy drinks.From a health perspective, both Lions Mane and Super Cocoa offer their own distinct advantages. Lion's Mane is a natural and mushroom-derived supplement that is believed to support brain health. It may have neuroprotective properties and help with nerve growth factor synthesis. Lion's Mane is an excellent choice for those seeking a natural cognitive boost and promoting long-term brain health.Super Cocoa, on the other hand, not only provides an energizing experience but also contains a blend of nootropic ingredients that support cognitive function. The inclusion of l-theanine, rhodiola, l-tyrosine, and alpha GPC creates a powerful combination that enhances focus, mental clarity, and overall productivity. Moreover, Super Cocoa's incorporation of natural ingredients and the absence of artificial additives make it a more wholesome option compared to traditional energy drinks.In conclusion, while Super Cocoa unquestionably takes the crown as the winner in this head-to-head comparison, Lions Mane should not be overlooked. Lions Mane is an exceptional supplement known for its potential cognitive-enhancing properties and overall brain health support. Super Cocoa stands out as a delightful nootropic coffee alternative, delivering sustained energy, exceptional flavor, and the added benefits of l-theanine, rhodiola, l-tyrosine, and alpha GPC.If you're seeking a supplement solely focused on cognitive enhancement, Lions Mane is an excellent choice. However, if you desire a multifaceted experience that includes energizing properties, an exquisite taste, and nootropic benefits, Super Cocoa is the clear winner. Elevate your cognitive capabilities and indulge in the delightful experience provided by Super Cocoa, while appreciating the unique cognitive support offered by Lions Mane

            Hay_Wife
            5.0 out of 5 stars Unlocking Mental Clarity: Lion's Mane & Super Cocoa
            Reviewed in the United States on June 28, 2023
            Size: 120 Count (Pack of 1)Verified Purchase
            Having explored the benefits of both Lions Mane and Super Cocoa, I must say that Super Cocoa emerges as the ultimate champion, delivering a unique blend of nootropic benefits, exceptional flavor, sustained energy, and a delightful coffee alternative. However, let's not undermine the value of Lions Mane, as it remains an excellent supplement in its own right.

            Let's start with Lions Mane. This remarkable supplement is derived from a medicinal mushroom and has gained popularity for its potential cognitive-enhancing properties. Lions Mane contains compounds that may support brain health, including hericenones and erinacines. It has been associated with improved focus, memory, and overall cognitive function. Taking Lions Mane as a supplement can be beneficial for those seeking a natural boost to their mental capabilities.

            On the other hand, Super Cocoa takes the concept of a coffee alternative to new heights by combining nootropic ingredients with a delicious taste. Super Cocoa offers a unique blend of l-theanine, rhodiola, l-tyrosine, and alpha GPC. L-theanine promotes relaxation and mental clarity, while rhodiola is known for its adaptogenic properties, helping the body better cope with stress. L-tyrosine supports dopamine production, which aids in focus and mood enhancement. Alpha GPC is a cholinergic compound that may enhance cognitive function and memory.

            What truly sets Super Cocoa apart is not only its nootropic ingredients but also its exceptional flavor and sustained energy without the crash. Super Cocoa provides an indulgent taste, reminiscent of a premium coffee blend, which makes it a delightful treat for the senses. The absence of artificial sweeteners or flavors ensures a more natural and authentic experience. Moreover, the combination of nootropic ingredients in Super Cocoa ensures sustained mental stamina, avoiding the crash that is commonly associated with traditional energy drinks.

            From a health perspective, both Lions Mane and Super Cocoa offer their own distinct advantages. Lion's Mane is a natural and mushroom-derived supplement that is believed to support brain health. It may have neuroprotective properties and help with nerve growth factor synthesis. Lion's Mane is an excellent choice for those seeking a natural cognitive boost and promoting long-term brain health.

            Super Cocoa, on the other hand, not only provides an energizing experience but also contains a blend of nootropic ingredients that support cognitive function. The inclusion of l-theanine, rhodiola, l-tyrosine, and alpha GPC creates a powerful combination that enhances focus, mental clarity, and overall productivity. Moreover, Super Cocoa's incorporation of natural ingredients and the absence of artificial additives make it a more wholesome option compared to traditional energy drinks.

            In conclusion, while Super Cocoa unquestionably takes the crown as the winner in this head-to-head comparison, Lions Mane should not be overlooked. Lions Mane is an exceptional supplement known for its potential cognitive-enhancing properties and overall brain health support. Super Cocoa stands out as a delightful nootropic coffee alternative, delivering sustained energy, exceptional flavor, and the added benefits of l-theanine, rhodiola, l-tyrosine, and alpha GPC.

            If you're seeking a supplement solely focused on cognitive enhancement, Lions Mane is an excellent choice. However, if you desire a multifaceted experience that includes energizing properties, an exquisite taste, and nootropic benefits, Super Cocoa is the clear winner. Elevate your cognitive capabilities and indulge in the delightful experience provided by Super Cocoa, while appreciating the unique cognitive support offered by Lions Mane
